Las Venas Abiertas de America Latina - The Open Veins of Latin America

An English translation of Las Venas Abiertas de America Latina, packaged together with the original en Espanol.

The book that Hugo Chavez gave to Barack seems to be flying off the shelves.

Saturday it went from an obscure 4xxx something to No. 7 at Amazon.
By Sunday it was at No. 2...

Lately, folks may not have the extra $35.00 to indulge their intellectual curiosity, and while I do not wish to detract from the impressive sales figures, I happened to find a copy on the intertubes this morning. If it's OK with the mods, I thought I'd share it with same.

Open Veins of Latin America - Five Centuries of the Pillage of a Continent by Eduardo Galeano (Jan 1, 1997)

